OL,4,CGun resembling Lego toy sparks backlash
OL,5,Cin US
OL,6, A US gun company is facing a backlash
OL,7, for producing a pistol that looks like
OL,8, a children's toy made of Lego.
OL,10,FCulper Precision said its customised
OL,11,FGlock weapon, named Block19, was
OL,12,Fdeveloped to "highlight the pure
OL,13,Fenjoyment of the shooting sports".
OL,15,FBut Danish toymaker Lego has written to
OL,16,Fthe company demanding that it stop
OL,17,Fproducing the weapon, which is covered
OL,18,Fin what looks like Lego bricks.
OL,20,FGun control campaigners described the
OL,21,Fpistol as irresponsible and dangerous.
